Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A present from South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You wanted one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare for you to watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a place where you can get 5000 yen just for sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to do it? Maybe not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's settled then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them you'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need it while you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Oreki residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Satoshi-kun? It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou? He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou! Satoshi-kun's on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, did you finish reading that book I lent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're done with it, can I get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I come over to pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After work, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After work, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Work? You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis's friend can't lifeguard the public pool today, so I'm going in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine you breaking a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over later to throw \Nsome cold water on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think all three of you would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I called them up as soon as I got off the phone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them they'd never get a chance to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}this{\i0} what you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't every day we go to the pool. Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, since we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit starin' at my woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray I don't have to deal with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda-san! Do something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Penalty game for Chitanda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my shift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to eat lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've made a better lunch if you'd told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell that to Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're talking about Houtarou, a sloth in human clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly he feels like working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't pass up seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of fun getting together like this, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, they just don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The pool and Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming trunks and Oreki don't mix either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sun and Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea and Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer and Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, why don't we get back to the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll clean up the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put the chairs back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go get you another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try it myself some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he wants to be a swimmer when he grows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have a future gold \Nmedalist in that pool right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple question of whether he has the ability to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's special, then he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's normal, then he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be special?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'm just a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} special, Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At least to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukube-san and Mayaka-san are special too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone I meet is special to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your personal opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the public opin{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with a personal opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about being special or normal compared to everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as they think you're special, then you're special!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
