Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.98,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(636,349.733)\fad(250,0)\b1\c&H030004&\fscx151\fscy156}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} special, Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with a personal opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki-kun, it's my shift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'm curious about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in your area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that woman with the red swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When we had finished eating, she had something white on her left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not on her ear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you notice something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw it by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "What about it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it were an earring or a stub?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone steps on it, they might get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki-san, could you help us look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the entire pool area? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was on her ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should ask her about it before we start looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit hard to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're asking anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't {\i1}you{\i0} ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, you're a lifeguard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That guy who was yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make a scene, so could you look for it discreetly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the other lifeguards look around the poolsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get you to check inside the pools?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. How should we look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We might want to split up and look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. What do you think, Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you at least pretend to be motivated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Otherwise you're getting paid for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At least decide how we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda-san and Mayaka handle the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou gets the water slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll take the diving board!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this job something you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you never gave it any thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your motto even for then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}sorry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At least complain or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to respond when people talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're boring otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in a bit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit slacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not slacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a marble, so I came here to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting depressed just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, I'd only get pissed off looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was annoying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying either way, so at the very least, be more like the old you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was better when you had some fight in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but we might not need to look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you've figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda, did you really see an earring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remember that there was something white on one of her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was only on one side, then it might be a stub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking about the kind of accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if what she saw was an accessory in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were wearing something on her ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't just hit her ears like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever was on her ear had to get on there without her noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But then what was on her ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, could you carry Ibara in your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem isn't who's holding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be like I'm a little kid! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because I want to see how a little kid would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do I have to do that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To prove my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By theory, you mean this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty strong, Chitanda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the way it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd usually put them on the shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I get down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that woman holding that little kid earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing they're mother and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what would happen if she held that kid while he was holding ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice cream could touch her ear just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's not on her ear now because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...it came off while she was swimming, or someone told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oreki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that how you do that is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattery's not going to get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've seen you so cynical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to know what to do when you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I haven't had a chance to thank you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki-san, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to cause you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who said it could have been an earring or stub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Just stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now that that's over, I'm getting kind of hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get some ice cream{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about ice cream{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you said you'd definitely have your manuscript done by today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's kind of done, but not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one way to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to put it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku-chan, we're going back, and you're finishing your manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you go until you're completely done with it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a bit left to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finish it on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'll believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan, Oreki, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they can finish that manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they say life is good when someone needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When you need someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I needed you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. It was a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that might not be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:22:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Oreki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,how did you know that the white thing was ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything white around here but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should go now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun with the rest of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your shift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
